casebody.data:
WW XPRESS, LLC d/b/a Worldwide Express, etc., Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Lindsey LOPEZ and Rebecca Wasif, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-1806 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 13, 2018 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and SALTER and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for writ of certiorari, and the response and reply thereto, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.

Upon consideration of respondents' motion for attorney's fees, it is ordered that said motion is conditionally granted and remanded to the trial court to fix amount, subject to determination of the prevailing party in the underlying trial court action.
